'''栗树山贵格会聚会所'''（Chestnut Hill Friends Meeting）是[[贵格会|贵格会]]的一个活跃的聚会所<ref name="Sharpe">{{cite news|last1=Sharpe|first1=Andy|title=First Quaker meetinghouse in 80 years set for Chestnut Hill-Mt. Airy border|url=http://www.flyingkitemedia.com/devnews/chfm1108.aspx|accessdate=2016-10-13|work=Flying Kite|date=2011-11-08|archive-date=2018-09-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180915150714/http://www.flyingkitemedia.com/devnews/chfm1108.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

该聚会于1924年11月9日在信徒罗伯特和伊丽莎白·亚纳尔家中开始<ref name="QMH">{{cite web|title=Chestnut Hill Monthly Meeting|url=http://quakermeetinghistory.com/content/chestnut-hill-monthly-meeting|website=Quaker Meeting History|accessdate=14 October 2016|archive-date=2019-04-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190428125431/http://quakermeetinghistory.com/content/chestnut-hill-monthly-meeting|dead-url=no}}</ref> 。

老聚会所建于1931年，位于[[宾夕法尼亚州|宾夕法尼亚州]][[费城|费城]]的栗树山社区的东美人鱼巷100号，为“牧场风格”，设计强调平等和反等级<ref name="HABS">{{cite web|title=CHESTNUT  HILL  FRIENDS  MEETING  HOUSE  100  E.  Mermaid  Lane  Philadelphia  HABS  No.  PA-6688|url=http://lcweb2.loc.gov/master/pnp/habshaer/pa/pa3900/pa3906/data/pa3906data.pdf|website=HISTORIC  AMERICAN  BUILDINGS  SURVEY|accessdate=2016-10-14|archive-date=2017-02-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170209235005/http://lcweb2.loc.gov/master/pnp/habshaer/pa/pa3900/pa3906/data/pa3906data.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

由于老聚会所不敷使用，2012-2013年，栗树山贵格会聚会所迁至东美人鱼巷20号的新聚会所，屋顶有贵格会艺术家[[詹姆斯·特瑞尔|詹姆斯·特瑞尔]]设计的天窗，这是第二个有如此设计的宗教场所<ref name="Meads">{{cite web|last1=Meads|first1=Helen|title=The Quaker Meaning of Light (and James Turrell's work)|url=http://goinsidetogreetthelight.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/Helen-Meads-Quaker-meaning-of-Light-_-JT-work_.pdf|website=www.academia.edu|date=2015|access-date=2017-01-17|archive-date=2020-05-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200513214742/https://goinsidetogreetthelight.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/Helen-Meads-Quaker-meaning-of-Light-_-JT-work_.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>。这是80年来费城第一个新建的聚会所<ref name="FCG">{{cite web|title=Go Inside and Greet the Light: Turrell Skyspace opens at the new Chestnut Hill meeting house|url=https://www.fgcquaker.org/news/go-inside-and-greet-light-turrell-skyspace-opens-new-chestnut-hill-meeting-house|website=Friends General Conference|accessdate=2016-10-13|archive-date=2020-10-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201031073800/https://www.fgcquaker.org/news/go-inside-and-greet-light-turrell-skyspace-opens-new-chestnut-hill-meeting-house|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

